{
  "stem": "3150.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not so much myself, my brother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went a few times, but mainly my brother and my father, when he was alive, used to go out once a week and bring food from a different guy that really supplied us.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The other guy was a Czech.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not a Czech farmer, not the same guy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They used to-- and he really fed us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Every week they used to go out and they used to prepare food and-- and bring us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we used to-- that's how we lived over there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we really existed mostly, you know-- in the winter, it's not-- it's not really that warm of weather there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it's-- things don't really spoil overnight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the winter months, it was no problem.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, it was cold enough there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- well, with-- in there with straw and blankets, really.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no-- no fire, nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We couldn't be seen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- we-- we couldn't be heard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we you know, really, that was very, very important.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Couldn't be seen and couldn't be heard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But even part of his family, what they had one kid was very young, he didn't know we were there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I don't know, they--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--were old enough there, they know we are-- that we were there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then-- and then of-- around Christmastime of '42, my father died.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we assume he had an ulcer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we assume it-- it started bleeding and he died from it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it's all-- we-- we all assume that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we buried them ourselves in that barn at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was in the-- we buried him in the barn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was, well, we buried-- we buried him our self.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
